column5: I am awake, but its getting tough to stay awake  God, I am old,
Pretty sad to spend new years eve on OFC! 25 Tom !
Not at all Wayne, not at all. Would rather be here than other places getting sh** faced, and having to spend money to get home. I am at home, and am getting sh** faced, lol.
Hey, I'll join the losers club. Sis is in bed, I'm playing poker, and I splurged tonight. Sipping Rickards Red. 19 minutes. Happy new years guys...
Playing ps2 with the family.  So, Im here also  Happy New Years GUYS!!!!!
5 minutes now.  I'm making earrings with the feathers DanC sent me.  Made some really cool ones tonight.  How exciting eh.  Cheers everyone  Joey
Yup I am here waiting for the ball to drop..  mmmm... Maclays  Gerritt

lol @ sad....Heck no i have spent most of my evening fighting with my windows movie maker,,,,,grrrrrrrrrrrrrr   I had my days OF being out all night on new yrs being the designated driver every year because i do not drink and still feeling like a i had a damn hang over the next morning......Something really wrong there....lol......fUNNY THING IS I REMEMBER when my mom hit my age and me and my sisters used to think she was old and boreing because she was not out partying like me and my sisters and now look at me......lol....same age as she was back then when we thought she was old and boreing.....lol & i am at home.  My boy's are all out doin there own thing i am quiet happy to be here at home...

Just Arnie and I hangin out celebrating the new years together.....My wife packed it in around 11.30,night night.......Me an old Arnie have sat through 11 new years together so far...Its nice to have him around....  Cheers !!!
Happy New Years folks, and when it comes to old and boring, I've got all of y'all beat.  I was in bed by 9, and asleep before 9:30.  Hope everyone that went out had a safe and fun evening.  Maureen
Ya, don't think I missed a whole lot, got up, the sun is peeking over the horizon, +7 out, going to mosey down to the Barrie docks and catch me a fishwich.
well now I feel bad for just playing gamecube with the wife and daughter and did not check in I guess I will have to turn in my OFC card.   Happy New Year everyone.
